President Uhuru Kenyatta Stands Best Chance Of Becoming Kenya's Prime Minister Under A New Constitutional Dispensation In 2022, Unless Anyone Unseats Him As Jubilee Party Leader! That Is The Latest Statement From Former Jubilee Vice?Chair David Murathe, In Apparent Response To Deputy President William Ruto's Recent Criticism Of His Earlier Suggestion That Kenyatta Should Continue His National Integration Agenda As Prime Minister, Under A New Constitutional Dispensation Through The Building Bridges Initiative. Tonight, Murimi Mwangi Reports On The Latest Murathe?Ruto Rivalry, And Explains Why The Dp's Handlers Are Cautioning The President Against Being Misguided By People They Claim Are Secretly Pursuing Selfish Agendas.